These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, pakistani, nigerian
1. the argentine is in an odd position##4
2. the nigerian is between the chinese and the argentine##2
3. the nigerian is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | argentine | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, pineapple, lime, raspberry
1. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pineapple | radish | raspberry | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, adventure, romance, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | sports | romance | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, swimming, basketball
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | skateboarding | golf | basketball | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skiing, tennis, basketball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | basketball | ice-hockey | tennis | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, japanese, turkish
1. the malaysian is on the far right##1
2. the malaysian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
3. the japanese is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | japanese | australian | turkish | malaysian |

