2. the fan of trance is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of dubstep##2
3. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | hip-hop | trance | dubstep |

