.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, trike, train
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | motorbike | train | subway |

