.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, banana, papaya, asparagus
1. the person eating banana is the person eating banana##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
3. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | papaya | asparagus | banana | tomato |

